---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StatusBadge from '../components/StatusBadge.astro';
---

<Layout title="University & Executive Ed" description="Level 3 — roadmap for adult learners, leadership and human–AI collaboration modules.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
      <span class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-navy-900 text-lg font-bold text-orange-400">3</span>
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Level 3</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 md:text-4xl">University &amp; Executive Education</h1>
      </div>
      <StatusBadge status="roadmap" label="Roadmap — AY 2027/28" />
    </div>
    <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg text-navy-700">
      The same methodological core — the Talento · Valore · Successo arc and
      Human-in-the-Loop by design — adapted for adult learners: leadership,
      innovation, and human–AI collaboration modules suitable for university and
      executive-education contexts.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section border-t border-navy-100">
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="card">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-orange-600">Adapted from Level 1–2</p>
        <p class="mt-3 font-bold text-navy-900">From "talent" to "professional identity"</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-navy-700">
          The Talento · Valore · Successo arc reframed as a leadership-development
          exercise: where does my contribution create value, and how do I measure
          success beyond conventional metrics?
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-orange-600">From Station 4</p>
        <p class="mt-3 font-bold text-navy-900">Human-in-the-Loop for decision-makers</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-navy-700">
          The same inspection posture pupils develop with comic strips — applied to
          AI-assisted decision-making, analysis, and reporting in a business context.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-orange-600">From the Teenager Circle</p>
        <p class="mt-3 font-bold text-navy-900">Near-peer / cross-cohort mentoring</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-navy-700">
          Exploring whether the near-peer instruction logic translates to
          cross-cohort mentoring formats in executive programmes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 card bg-navy-950 text-navy-50">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-orange-400">Status — honestly stated</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-navy-100">
        This level is a <strong>roadmap stub</strong>, not a built product. It is
        included here to show how the same architecture extends to university and
        executive-education audiences — a natural direction for the Phase II research
        collaboration with INSEAD, AY 2027/28 and beyond. Nothing on this page
        represents a committed deliverable or partnership.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section border-t border-navy-100 text-center">
    <a href="/industry" class="btn-primary">See Level 4 — Industry →</a>
  </div>
</Layout>
